Resources for Development:

For making new Fences:
  Google Awareness API: https://developers.google.com/awareness 
 
For pushing notifications:
  Google Notidification API: https://developer.android.com/training/notify-user/build-notification
  
Online database and other services:
  Firebase guides: https://firebase.google.com/docs/guides
  
  
Future Tasks:

* Create Multiple Location Fences based in user input. User should be able to input addresses or location pin, and the app should perform
  address translation to convert that into coordinates.
* Implement Login functionality. Use firebase to assign each user with  unique ID to label their personalized data in the database. 
  Implemnt login using phone's default authentication method.
 
  
  
  
  

  
